        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Climate Readiness Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense to report on the national security implications associated with climate change and strategies and approaches for responding to climate change. The report must be submitted in an unclassified form, but may contain a classified annex.</p>]]>
        </text>
